<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這就是線索的雕塑嗎～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />同樣的內容卻用了三種語言來記錄，<delay20 />
看來是想傳達重要的事情呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />會是什麼事呢？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難道是愛的告白嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />實在是太美了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那追求細節的衣物皺摺表現，<delay20 />
讓人完全無法想像這是座雕刻<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />此外，無法看見女神的表情，<delay20 />
反而更加刺激了我的想像力，<delay20 />
讓人為之傾倒<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在那鋼鐵般的肉體上隆起的肌肉，<delay20 />
看起來真是厲害啊～<10_4 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過我脫光後，<delay20 />也不會輸給它就是了！</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒想到能親眼見到實物，我太感動了～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來吧，<delay20 />用你那安穩的微笑，<delay20 />
來注視著<tag a="110" b="10" />吧<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />如果我也像這幅畫一樣，<delay20 />　
一絲不掛地被展示在這裡<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />會慌張的應該不是天使，<delay20 />而是<colour id="3" />傅達<colour id="65535" />吧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈～！</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />經過了足以讓畫褪色的漫長歲月，<delay20 />
這幅畫此刻就展示在我眼前<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這件事本身就像是奇蹟一樣呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好大的一幅畫啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這幅畫值得注目的地方，<delay20 />
應該是上面描繪了很多女孩子吧。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀～<delay frames="40" />這幅畫裡的女性，<delay20 />
看起來真是英姿煥發呢。<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的好帥氣啊～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果真有這樣的女性，<delay20 />
我一定會跟隨她到天涯海角的～</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Hi——！<delay20 />那邊那位小姐！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是來自<tag a="110" b="9" />的<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="10" />喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我一見到如此美麗的女性，<delay20 />
就忍不住出聲搭訕了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算這只是個藝術品也一樣<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />神秘的名畫<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是一幅充滿著神秘色彩的畫啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這幅畫並非一昧地表現黑暗深沉，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而是清楚地表達出悲觀主義思想，令人印象深刻。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ColdChill" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺這景象似乎會出現在今晚的夢裡<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看著這幅和煦的名畫，<delay20 />
心靈也跟著沉澱了下來呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看著它時我總有一種感覺，<delay20 />
彷彿我正在看著<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="8" />的景色一樣<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這幅閃爍的名畫有著一種奇妙的魅力，<delay frames="40" />
彷彿要將凝視它的人吸入畫中<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在那獨特的筆觸下，<delay20 />雖然看起來只是
一幅普通的風景畫，<delay20 />但是卻能從中
清楚地感受到它所傳達的訊息呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這幅磅礡的名畫，<delay20 />
生動地表現出洶湧的海浪，<delay20 />
真是讓人感動啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原來宏偉的藝術，不僅僅是只有魄力，<delay20 />
而且能讓人獲得其中所蘊含的力量<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺就像是自己和作者心靈相通了。</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這就是武士的雕塑嗎<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是做工細緻且栩栩如生，<delay20 />
彷彿下一秒就會自己動起來呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />奇怪<tag a="110" b="0" />它剛才動了一下？<10_4 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不對，<delay20 />那怎麼可能嘛，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這就是遠古的雕塑嗎<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明明是相當古老的作品，
卻保存得很好呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我聽說似曾相識的雕塑<delay20 />
其作品背景眾說紛紜，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但它應該是正在煩惱著什麼吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />人在猶豫時，不要想太多，<delay20 />
總之先行動就對了，<delay frames="40" /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈～！</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<tag a="110" b="4" />！我聽說囉，
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個作品是你捐給博物館的對吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多虧了你，我才有機會接觸藝術的世界，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />並獲得如此美好的體驗喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>